Package sep.gaia.resources.poi

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    POICache
    Defines a class for caching Point-Of-Interests (POI) in memory.
    POICategory
    Represents a major-category for point-of-interests.
    POIFilter
    Represents a set of conditions a POI must fulfill to be part of the system with the respective filter.
    POILoaderWorker
    A class for asyncroniously performing a part of request for POIs.
    POIManager
    Manages PointOfInterest-objects using appropriate major- and sub-categories.
    PointOfInterest
    Represents a geographical point with certain attributes that might be of interest for a user.
    POIQuery
    A query describing POIs to be generated by a loader.
    POISet
    A set of PointOfInterest-objects.
    POIWorkerFactory
    Class for generating new workers.
    SubCategory
    Bean-class for describing a sub-category of POIs.
    Way
    Describes a way having certain attributes and being composed of multiple nodes.
